<HEAD>U.N. Confirms Cordovez Was Offered Foreign Minister's Post</HEAD>
<DATELINE>UNITED NATIONS (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Undersecretary-General Diego Cordovez has
been offered the post of foreign minister of Ecuador in the
government of President-Elect Roderigo Borja, the United Nations
confirmed Thursday.
   Francois Giuliani, spokesman for Secretary-General Javier Perez
de Cuellar, told reporters Cordovez informed the U.N. chief several
