aggravated assault and battery after allegedly beating his wife
with a pipe. He also was charged with firing a gun into a car while
she was inside.
   Mrs. Brown was arrested April 9 in nearby Augusta, Ga., on drug
charges.
   Brown, known to fans as the ``Godfather of Soul,'' won his
second Grammy award last year for his recording of ``Living in
America.''
